name: A Visual Delight #3
description:
This photograph is taken at Bagore-ki-Haveli, Udaipur. It is right on the waterfront of Lake Pichola at Gangori Ghat. Amar Chand Badwa, the Prime Minister of Mewar, built it in the eighteenth century.

This gate is a masterpiece work of artists of those times!! The work we see on this gate is so fine, handmade done by artists in eighteen century...
